summary_gpt: The company has announced the transfer of unclaimed dividends from shareholders whose shares have been dormant for over seven years to the Investor Education and Protection Fund (IEPF), with the final dividend for FY 2017-18 scheduled for transfer by September 26, 2025. Notifications have been published in newspapers and sent to affected shareholders as per regulatory requirements.

Jyothy Labs Limited has announced a conference call scheduled for May 12, 2025, to discuss its Q4 FY25 financial results and future outlook, with details available on their website and through registered links. The company is complying with SEBI regulations by informing investors and analysts about this event.

Jyothy Labs Limited has scheduled a Board meeting on May 12, 2025, to approve the audited financial results for the quarter and year ended March 31, 2025, and to consider dividend recommendations for FY 2024-25. The results and decisions will be disclosed on their website and to investors.
